add_packet:
this programe is to add a packet header to a file.

The packet header is consist of:
packet_flg     : 8 bytes --semptian

Version        :
major          : 1 byte     --1
revision       : 1 byte     --1
build          : 2 bytes    --1124

time           :
year           : 2 bytes    --2011
month          : 1 byte     --11
day            : 1 byte     --28
hour           : 1 byte     --16
minute         : 1 byte     --30
sencond        : 1 byte     --23

packet_length  : 1 byte     --64
file_length    : 4 bytes    --232323

md5            : 32 bytes   --8cca9e22a868aeafc29435208eb1d4f4

packet header: 64 bytes
       0         1          2           3         4          5           6        7
 -----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
0|                               Packet                 Flg                              |
 |----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
1|   Major  |   Revis  |         Build       |            Reserved                       |
 |----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
2|          Year       |    Month |    Day   |   hour   |   minute |   second | Reserved |
 |----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
3|packet_len|           Reserved             |           File      Length                |
 |----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
4|          |          |          |          |          |          |          |          |
 |----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
5|          |          |          |          |          |          |          |          |
 |----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
6|          |          |          |          |          |          |          |          |
 |----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
7|          |          |          |          |          |          |          |          |
 |----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

